  "description": "You must tell DVLA if you have a severe communication disorder and it affects your driving - download the correct form to let them know",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You must tell DVLA if your severe communication disorder affects your ability to drive safely.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you do not tell DVLA about a condition that affects your driving. You may be prosecuted if you’re involved in an accident as a result.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Ask your doctor if you’re not sure if your severe communication disorder will affect your driving.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"car-or-motorcycle-licence\">Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/government/publications/a1-report-your-medical-condition\">Fill in form A1</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"bus-coach-or-lorry-licence\">Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/government/publications/report-your-medical-condition-form-a1v\">Fill in form A1V</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n",
